<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-69-0961 </DOCNO><TEXT>Is the pot of gold cracking up? The news this week that the site of theOk Tedi project's tailings dam is in the process of being swamped bya massive landslip certainly suggests some very major problems. Beforeexamining the question and the implications of this week's news further,it might be useful, first, to try and explain what a tailings dam isand why it is vital to the project and, second, to give a brief summaryof the history of the tailings dam so far.</TEXT></DOC>